name: Young Love
overview: The Young family – millennial parents Stephen and Angela, their daughter Zuri and her pet cat Rocky – juggle careers, marriage, parenthood, social issues and multi-generational dynamics while striving to make a better life for themselves.
tagline: A little bit of work and a whole lot of love.

episodes.name: Self Love
episodes.overview: While a cancer-free Angela returns to work, Stephen attempts to impress rapper Lil Ankh, and a disappointed Zuri attends a school fundraiser alone.

episodes.name: Just Love
episodes.overview: As Angela attempts to tackle her lofty list of goals, Stephen struggles to stay focused on an upcoming deadline.

episodes.name: Work Love
episodes.overview: While Angela’s business booms, Lil Ankh takes Stephen for a ride, and Zuri finds herself roped into her grandparents’ epic battle of the sexes.

episodes.name: Charity Love
episodes.overview: When Zuri invites her friend’s family to stay with them, Angela trades in kindness for clout. Later, Stephen attempts to bond with his nephew.

episodes.name: Jingle Love
episodes.overview: After Lil Ankh disses his beats, Stephen begins to work for a questionable marketing firm, while Angela pretends to be rich to impress a new client.

episodes.name: Lost Love
episodes.overview: Facing an uncertain future, Stephen contemplates quitting music, while Angela struggles to find her true passion, and Zuri attempts a career as an oracle.

episodes.name: Game Love
episodes.overview: While Stephen succumbs to the allure of video games, a skeptical Angela joins forces with Gigi to fight back against a shady pyramid scheme.

episodes.name: Chicago Love
episodes.overview: While Stephen and Angela attempt to make the most of a rare free day, Amir drags Zuri on a rule-breaking adventure.

episodes.name: Protest Love
episodes.overview: With her bosses out of town, Angela takes control of the salon, while Zuri finds her calling as a playground activist.

episodes.name: Generational Love
episodes.overview: As Angela frets over her connection with an increasingly distant Zuri during a school field trip, Stephen attempts to turn Amir into a sneaker head.

episodes.name: Faith Love
episodes.overview: After a trip to church, Zuri casts a heavenly spell on her classmates, while Angela and Stephen turn to financial advisor for help with their bills.

episodes.name: Love Love
episodes.overview: When Zuri acts out, Angela and Stephen finally begin to consider marriage – but creeping doubts cause the couple to question their impending nuptials.
